Mohobbat [E]hai sanam\n\n[Am]Durr kbhi [F]jake [Dm]nhi ka[E]rna si[Am]tam\n[Dm]Tu he du[G]a [C]tu he daw[F]aa\n\nOr [Em]teri band[G]agi me dil [F]gulaam ban g[Am]aya\n[Am]Humne to yunhi gungun[G]aaya tha tujhe\n\n[F]Tu to shayaraana ka[G]lam ban g[Am]ya\n[Am]Humne rait pe yuhi [G]feri thi ungliyan\n\n[F]Kya karu ittefaaq se tera [G]naam ban [Am]gya\n\nTu [Dm]mera phla-phla [F]pyar ban gya\n\n[Am]Humne rait pe yuhi [G]feri thi ungliyan\n\n[F]Kya karu ittefaaq se tera [G]naam ban [Am]gya\n: Humne rait pe is a very amorous song with a lot of passion and love. The lyrics are extremely conversational and metaphorical. With the use of some Urdu words in between the verses , the song has a very rich and profound meaning. Love has been shown in a very poetic manner in this melody. The song has a very pacifying music and this melody has no crests or troughs in between. Tony has showed us his genius once again in this number. His dulcet and gentle voice is very captivating and it is for him that we are bound to come back to this track again and again and listen to it on loop. Neha is undoubtedly bewitching and her melodious vocals are just beyond praise. Filmed on the handsome Karanveer and the stunning Priya, their on screen chemistry is just sizzling to watch and this video is a treat to the eyes. Humne rait pe is perfect for a romantic dinner date or a long drive with your better half. And well, if you’re planning to confess your passionate love to your someone special whom you still haven’t yet told about your feelings, then say them loud by playing this song to her and see how she falls in love with you within a few moments.\n: Humne Rait Pe Yuhi Pheri Thi Ungliyaan\n: Neha Kakkar & Tony Kakkar\n\n\n: Hume Tumse Pyaar Kitna\n\n\n Sajan Agarwal\n\n\n: Tony Kakkar\n\n\n: June 2019\n\n\n: India\n\n\n: Hindi\n\n\n: T-Series\'','\'New\'','Humne-Rait-Pe-Chords-with-Strum---Guitar---Neha-Kakkar---Tony-Kakkar---Abhijeet','C Major,D Minor','new','new','new','C Major','new','D uud udu'),(243,'\'Zindagi Di Paudi Guitar Chords with Strumming | Millind Gaba - Abhijeet\'','\'Love is intensely beautiful and sweet but also has it’s own ups and downs and storms and sunshine. Zindagi di paudi from the album “Blessed” justifies this statement in a very melodious manner. Sung by the mellifluous Millind Gaba, the track has been composed and penned by the versatile Nirmaan. This song is from the filmi soundtrack genre and uses the guitars , strings and the flutes quite artfully. Zindagi di paudi chords are simple and do not require much skills to be played by the beginners. The guitar chords of Zindagi di paudi are four in number and they are Am, E, D, Bm, A. The capo position is in the 4th fret. The chords of Zindagi di paudi have a harmonious progression and follow the strumming pattern of D UDUD UDUD DU. The track has a moderately paced tempo with a signature 4/4 beat and has been played in the Am scale.\n: D UDUD UDUD DU\nd – Down Stroke on lower three strings\n\nD – Down Strum\n\nU – Up Strum\n\nC – Chuck/Mute Effect\n: Accurate & Verified by Team\n: 4\n\n\n: 4th Fret\n\n\n: Am, E, D, Bm, A\n\n\n: D UDUD UDUD DU\n[Am]Zindagi Di Paudi Jithe Tak Chadhaange\n\nTere [E]Naal Chadaange\n\n[Am]Sukh Hove Dukh Hove Dhunp Chaanv\n\nTere [E]Naal Khadaange\n[D]Me Ohna Cho Nhi Jo Waada Krde\n\nNayi Poora Wich [E]Dol Jaande Ne\n\n[D]Me Ohda Cho Nhi Jo Bohte Bandey Ne\n\nSachhe [E]Jhuth Bol Jande Ne\n[D]Jithe V Rahenge Khushi He Rahaange\n\n[Bm]Dukh Aya Koyi Ohde [E]Naal Ladaange\n[Am]Zindagi Di Paudi Jithe Tak Chadhaange\n\nTere [E]Naal Chadhaange\n\n[Am]Sukh Hove Dukh Hove Dhoop Chaaw\n\nTere [E]Naal Khadhange\n[A]Mehal Da Waada Nai Krda Me\n\n[D]Ek Chota Ja [E]Ghar Hona\n\nOh… [A]Mehal Da Waada Nai Karda Me\n\n[D]Ek Chota Ja [E]Ghar Hona\n[A]Laakh Croran Nai Judne Ne\n\n[D]Hazaaran Wich He [E]Sir Hona\n[D]Main Ohna Cho Nhi Jo Tennu Pon Layi\n\nWaade-Waade [E]Khwaab Dikhaaye\n\n[D]Main Ohna Cho Nhi Jo Tennu Pon Layi\n\nAmbraan To [E]Taare Laaike Aye\n[D]Ohna He