eghdeep Bose\n: Fakeera is the romantic song of the year. There is a feeling of freshness and newness in the melody and that is what makes this track so endearing to the audience. Like Pareshan from Ishaqzaade, I Love You from Bodyguard, Kya Karun from Barfi and Te Amo from Dum Maro Dum; Fakeera can be added to this list of songs that talk about this new and crazy feeling of falling in love. The song is intensely serenading with a very amorous sensation about it. Shot in a college set, this song has been filmed on the pretty Ananya Pandey and the talented Tiger Shroff. . This film is a debut for Ananya and her romance with Tiger on-screen is very natural and sizzling and it is indeed a delight to watch. Fakeera is a song that will continue to entice us even after decades and this track will remain evergreen forever. The song is ideal for you if you are planning to serenade with your lover on a romantic date, or if you are in solitude and want to get engrossed in the thoughts of your better half. And if you have not yet told her those three golden words, then say it out with this song and strum those simple chords on your guitar and make her go all crazy about you.\'','\'New\'','Student-of-the-Year-2--Fakira-Guitar-Chords-with-Capo-by-Sanam---Abhijeet','C Major,D Minor','new','new','new','C Major','new','D uud udu'),(248,'\'RAETH: Bhula Do Bhula Do Guitar Chords - Abhijeet\'','\'Some songs will never be forgotten. Even if they have been released decades back, these songs never age and remain as timeless masterpieces. Bhula Do by Raeth is that classic song. Sung by Wajhi Farooki, this melody has been composed and penned by the entire band- Raeth. This song uses the guitars and the drums to create the mesmerising music. Bhula Do is a wonderful guitar based track with novice level chords that the beginners can pick up with ease. The progression of the chords is harmonious and this song has a fast paced tempo with a signature 4/4 beat. The soundtrack is from the pop genr