s. It is for him that we are forced to come back to this track again and again. The video of this song features the superstar Rajesh Khanna and the elegant Nanda and is just a delight to watch. The melody harmonises well with the romantic and jovial mood. And if you want to win your girl in the old school way, then strum and play this mesmerising track on your guitar to her and see how she falls head over heels in love with you.\'','\'New\'','Gulabi-Aankhen-Chords-with-Guitar-Strumming-Pattern---Atif-Aslam-R-D-Burman---Abhijeet','C Major,D Minor','new','new','new','C Major','new','D uud udu'),(492,'\'Sona Mohapatra - Anhad Naad Guitar Chords With Strumming Pattern - Lal Pari Mastani - Abhijeet\'','\': Presenting the guitar chords of  latest song by Sona Mohapatra – Anhad Naad. This beautiful song is sung by Sona Mohapatra, and the lyrics is penned by Munna Dhiman while the song composition is done by Ram Sampat. The scale of this song is in G major. If you would like to play the Coke Studio version of this song then you would need to use A Major as the scale and can change the chords of whole song as per the Scale. If we talk about the strumming pattern for this song then you can try D UUD D where D is Down Strum and U is Up Strum. We’ve used total 4 Chords to play Anhad Naad Song of Sona Mohaptra – G, D, C, and Am Chord. Below we’ve shared the Anhad Naad Chords. Please let us know if you find any problem in playing the chords of this song.\n \n: D UUD D\nD – Down Strum\n\nU – Up Strum\n: G Major\n\n\n: G, D, C, Am\n[D] Hund Me Anhad\n\nNaad [G] Bajaya\n\n[D] Apne Dil Da [G] Haaal Sunaya\n\n[D] Hund Me Anhad\n\n[G] Naad [Am] Bajaaya\n\n[D] Apne Dil Da [G] Haal Sunaya\n[C] Haal Suna Ke Lufto [Am] Paaya\n\n[C] Jo Barkha Vich Ped [D] Nahahya\n\nHai e e\n\n[C] Haal Suna Ke Lufto [Am] Paya\n\n[C] Jo Barkha Vich Ped [D] Nahahya\n[G] Rom Rom Mere Ghungroo [Am] Chankey\n\nHo o o o..\n\n[G] Rom Rom Mere Ghungroo Chankey\n\n[Am] Log Kahe [G] Mastana [D] Ayaa\n[D] Hund Main An